{"tid":325624,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗好食仲識講乜嘢？ 個個都好膚淺","createTime":"2017-07-17T10:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T02:39:18.000Z","uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6322d76117e26a62063361c23aaa7195fef495a0","tid":325624,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"睇旅遊節目見到啲人食嘢， 浮誇到仆街， 擺咗入口就喺度鳩叫呱呱呱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 好撚戇鳩。<br />\n見到電視節目啲藝人又係戇鳩鳩， 未擺入口已經叫定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁話好食好食好食好食好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實除咗甜咗啲，鹹咗啲， 好爽，好腍， 一啲較為具體嘅形容， 又或者係將該樣餸同另外一樣人人都知嘅去比較之外， 仲有啲乜嘢可以形容得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？"},{"pid":"1d82524156f9d3c4e24cb598a26c481c26a9344e","tid":325624,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"肉嘅處理手法，質感，蔬菜嘅處理，煮嘅時間等等....好多可以講，班戇鳩整係識甜呀甜呀，好食呀好食...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88238cf96a1b1680c95f3d530ce240288ab561f5","tid":325624,"uid":117302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:15:03.000Z","msg":"你睇詹姆士主持d旅遊節目，佢講得幾好"},{"pid":"2b7af318b1daf97c3cbeb973597ac693b6ae6078","tid":325624,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"聽到口感兩個字就想屌鳩班港女主持"},{"pid":"be109f29a9a89e55d6e38c25c3fdef2340834bc1","tid":325624,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:17:49.000Z","msg":"隱世極邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83eb5d28487cac8af9212df78e8fb94837400685","tid":325624,"uid":93588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"its fking <span style=\"font